{"tid":97310,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"青山醫院覆診揮手區","createTime":"2017-01-27T14:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T16:39:00.000Z","uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7860e1d52907a9825f587f485dc15fb040c56351","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"明心樓思覺失調服務<br />\n<br />\n之前我冇返去覆診 當然亦都冇食藥<br />\n<br />\n老母見咁樣都直情唔幫我返去拎藥<br />\n<br />\n最近連醫生都廢鬼事理我<br />\n因為我唔係真嚴重果D<br />\n<br />\n於是佢決定放過我<br />\n好似隔多一排先返去見佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知CLOSE得FILE未<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n明心樓CAFE的燒賣牛肉魚蛋腸粉真係好好食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597b5b83f4447d5364ea6066924cf918c5dd3c7e","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"之前社康姑娘喺我返工時間打過黎手機<br />\n<br />\n嚇得我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fceb1968d83602e8f7419e1ff83bd7add44d46","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"之前OPEN DAY去睇下<br />\n<br />\n本來想入明心樓食燒賣<br />\n<br />\n不過冇開門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6b31c201ff78b7884577adee8b1952f3d0cfd9","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"D人聽到去青山睇醫生好似最嚴重程度咁<br />\n<br />\n但講真跟地區啫<br />\n<br />\n新界西醫院聯網咪青山囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df73298b332ec23af2a992d9af403b9c9190ed74","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:34:22.000Z","msg":"我唔算真係嚴重到落街劈友果D<br />\n<br />\n如果係既話我就連DSE都考唔到啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c954a0bfbab77bac467ee860b27fca9aa1d3ee94","tid":97310,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好返未呀你 睇臨床心理學家好過食精神科藥啦！"},{"pid":"1e22b47c230aa244aabfbacc30a3dd94e74bb956","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"如果如果如果如果<br />\n我成世就會唔同"},{"pid":"7967d917f536823e93407cb5eb23727078dea869","tid":97310,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"食得藥多就會依賴<br />\n<br />\n靠行為治療同心理輔導啦！"},{"pid":"d22fa1671ecd766d658bf0bee823e9da1205eb2c","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好返未呀你 睇臨床心理學家好過食精神科藥啦！</blockquote><br />\n唔洗喇<br />\n其實我而家都冇乜野<br />\n<br />\n真係有野果陣係唔想...唔敢出街<br />\n<br />\n而家行葵廣西九都冇事啦"},{"pid":"4d7c7b492072c0d160171c7dc6d9c78fc2f65767","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食得藥多就會依賴<br />\n<br />\n靠行為治療同心理輔導啦！</blockquote><br />\n唔想同輔導講野<br />\n<br />\n15年見過十次以下<br />\n上年+今年見過兩次<br />\n<br />\n講真過後諗返<br />\n兩條友都講過左D野 令我回想返起會唔高興<br />\n<br />\n無謂浪費錢講無謂野"},{"pid":"1afdbcbdb485cafdcfe02dbe31ab928087e7d8ef","tid":97310,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac328375ce9d8cd9d122510579833f61783e6554","tid":97310,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}